featured_reviews.review_id:
It's a beautiful mosque at Jagatsukh. The place can be accessed through road  You can get down at Jagatsukh chowk on Kullu nagar road
This is a mosque with a capacity of 100-150 people can pray at a time  The mosque also has a lawn which is used for Jumma prayer or Annual prayer of Eid.

featured_reviews.review_id:
The Only Masjid in Manali to my knowledge.
Approx. 8KM from Manali Bazar.
People who are in manali looking for Jumah Namaz,  this is the right place.
Jumah Namaz is by 2pm.

featured_reviews.review_id:
The only place near Manali to perform prayer.
Masjid is under 10 km from Manali bus stop.
I visited there on January 2018 and the time for Juma Namaz was 2:00pm. Namaz time table is also attached. And to go to this place is quite is easy , all you need to take a local bus from Manali bus stop to Jagatsukh.
